These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, begonia
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, peach, pomegranate
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, entrepreneur, photographer
House: ranch-style, wooden, farmhouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, family
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, tiparillo, montecristo
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, poker
 1. the siglo-smoker is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the farmhouse house is the person eating pomegranate##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
 4. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the person playing poker##1
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person playing chess and the person playing scrabble##2
 8. the coach is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
 9. the person who growsorchid is the ranch-style house##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
11. the person playing scrabble is the photographer##1
12. the person watching family movies is the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3       |
| Flower      | begonia     | dahlia        | orchid         |
| Food         | pomegranate  | peach | blueberry       |
| Job           | photographer | coach      | entrepreneur |
| House   | farmhouse       | wooden     | ranch-style          |
| Movie-Genre           | documentary   | comedy        | family       |
| Cigar         | montecristo   | tiparillo    | siglo     |
| Game     | scrabble       | poker      | chess         |

