.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra, game
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, drawing, filmmaking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, marigold
There 3 different types of food: amberrot, peach, pomegranate
House: farmhouse, futuristic, cottage
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, polish
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, amber, apricot
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person eating amberrot##1
 2. the indonesian is on the left of the argentine##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 5. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 7. the person who likes amber is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 8. the argentine is between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes lavender##2
 9. the person who growsmarigold is the person eating pomegranate##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
11. the person who likes apricot is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the cottage house is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |
| Cigar      | game   | alhambra     | tiparillo                |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping  | drawing            |
| Flower           | amaryllis  | dahlia   | marigold |
