The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, june, january
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, pony
City: miami, boston, nizza
House: tower, townhouse, futuristic
 1. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the tower house##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is the dannemann-smoker##1
 8. the person eating lime is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster    | dannemann  | havana |
| Beverage   | juice | milk  | soy-milk    |
| Food   | grapes    | lime  | carrot       |
