The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, marigold
3 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, red, green
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, february, march
City: san-francisco, venice, boston
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, spanish, german
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person playing go##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 6. the indian is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 8. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the german is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is between the person traveling to boston and the person who likes green##2
11. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3        |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | milk        | cola           |
| Flower          | aconite | marigold   | dahlia       |
| Game         | snooker | billiard | go         |
