.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-3-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy, daisy
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, fishing, writing
City: paris, new-york, miami
House: palace, modern, wooden
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, grapefruit, garlic
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, july, november
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, funk
 1. the fan of dubstep is the person eating garlic##1
 2. the wooden house is the person who growspoppy##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 4. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1
 5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the palace house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |       3       |
| Flower      | daisy         | begonia | poppy |
| Hobby         | dancing       | writing     | fishing       |
| City           | miami     | new-york      | paris     |
| House   | modern       | palace     | wooden       |
| Food   | grapefruit         | cauliflower  | garlic      |
| Birthday           | january           | november        | july    |
| Music-Genre         | funk | indie    | dubstep    |

