There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, japanese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, sailing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, aristoff, prince
 1. the brazilian is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the victorian house##1
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the japanese is on the far left##1
10. the victorian house is the person who growsbegonia##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the art-deco house##1
12. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
