City: venice, prague, paris
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, iris, bellflower
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, townhouse
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, colombian, australian
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the australian is between the person who growsiris and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the townhouse house##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 6. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person playing go##2
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
10. the colombian is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
