The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, august, november
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, emerald, fuchsia
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, goldfish
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the fan of classical##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person eating lettuce is the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the person who likes mauve is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person playing billiard##2
 7. the person who likes emerald is the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating grapes is the fan of punk##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
