 1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
 2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is the art-deco house##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person playing poker##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person eating pepper is the person drinking cola##1
 9. the art-deco house is the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person playing chess is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the cottage house is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the scooter##1
13. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

