.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-3-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, hot-chocolate
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, begonia
There 3 different types of food: apricot, raspberry, plum
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, go
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, tiparillo, game
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, cat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, cricket, handball
 1. the owner of the cat is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the person eating apricot is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person playing domino##2
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the blend-smoker and the person eating raspberry##2
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 9. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | coffee       | 7up        | hot-chocolate |
| Flower         | begonia      | tulip     | lily         |
| Food           | plum | apricot | raspberry     |
| Game   | domino      | go  | scrabble         |
| Cigar   | blend          | tiparillo      | game          |
| Pet   | horse       | rabbit     | cat      |
| Sport     | handball       | cricket | cycling      |

