The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, sports
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, coffee
3 different games are played: domino, go, bridge
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival, victorian
 1. the victorian house is between the dunhill-smoker and the person drinking sprite##2
