 3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person drinking juice is the person playing go##1
 5. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
